data.description: Charming, well-maintained 1227 sq ft, 2 bedroom/2 bathroom townhouse.  Many upgrades throughout including Roof Replacement 5 years ago, Pipes Replaced (No Galvanized Pipes), New Clear Story Windows and Skylights in Indoor Atrium, Wood Flooring and Ceiling Fans.  Large Primary Suite, w/ Barn Doors, Newer Shower. Large Garage with Storage Room and Laundry Room. Private Courtyard faces the lush and serene Pool area with Two Pools (heated and not heated).  Close to schools, shopping, restaurants & more. Don't miss this beautiful home.  A must see!
